<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/23409413">为什么淘宝网上的这些牛排很便宜？另外可以去哪里买靠谱的牛排？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="106608727"
data-atoken="420969604"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1529387696"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="0"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/23409413/answer/420969604">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="106608727">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="420969604">
